<div class="case-story__chapter">
  <h2>Research &amp; Insight</h2>
  <p>I kicked off the project with an experience audit. This helped me get acquainted to their unique the checkout experience.</p>
  <p>The existing checkout was divided into four screens:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Billing Address</li>
    <li>Shipping Information</li>
    <li>Order Review</li>
    <li>Payment</li>
  </ol>
  <p>The second screen&mdash;shipping information&mdash;was the biggest offender with two major issues: information duplication and unnecessary friction.</p>
